  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educating Afghans through Radio/TV</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We have combined projects Radio Meraj and TV Meraj! Reaching many more Afghans with education to empower them to improve their lives. Some people live too far from an AIL Learning Center or do not feel safe to travel. Reaching these people with education through broadcast media is an effective means and a popular solution. Radio Meraj has been going since 2015 providing educational programs and TV Meraj will soon start broadcasting. Both stations are housed in AIL&apos;s Herat office building.</narrative>
  </description>
